  "description": "The atmospheric, calmer version of the FLASH recipe — electrical phenomena observed from a distance. Noise src1 through BP (proc1=BP, 1500 Hz, reso=0.68) — the resonance is present but not threatening. gestureMode=3, flashTrigger=0.65 (lower threshold, gentler trigger). proc2=LP (5500 Hz) keeps considerable brightness — this is a high-altitude electrical atmosphere, thin air. aggression=0.38 — present but meditative. Reverb dominant (fx1=Reverb, 0.62 mix, 0.82 param) creates enormous space around the sparks. LFO->FilterCutoff (0.18 Hz, slow atmospheric sweep), Env->Volume (controlled surge), Velocity->FilterReso (responsive but gentle), Aftertouch->FXMix. MOVEMENT macro 0.32, CHARACTER 0.35.",
